  "texts": [
    "Then, the extracted features are sequenced and passed to the LSTM network for classification.",
    "Equipped with the ability to manage sequential data and long-term dependencies, the LSTM can process image features over time.",
    "Using its gates to control how information flows, the LSTM can learn patterns across the sequence of frames.",
    "Thus, combining feature extraction via CNN and sequence pattern learning through LSTM enables the system to recognize and classify activities effectively in real-time video streams.",
    "The CNN-LSTM approach has shown promising results in real-world applications, detecting suspicious activities at 10-13 frames-per-second in real-time under various conditions."
  ],
